 management, always with an entrepreneurial approach.\r\n      </p>\r\n      <p>TAN pursues investments with a significant return and with a 3 to 5 years time horizon.\r\n      </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tb\" id=\"tab2\">\r\n      <h1>TAN PROJECTS\r\n      </h1>\r\n      <p>Through its network and the managerial skills developed over the years, TAN is able to identify opportunities in the market and to exploit them by developing new business projects of its own Such investments also have a medium to long-term horizon.\r\n      </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tb\" id=\"tab3\">\r\n      <h1>ADVISORY\r\n      </h1>\r\n      <p>TAN, through its management company TAN Advisory, provides financial and strategic consulting services to third parties, leveraging on the cross-sectorial and cross-functional experience of its team, acquired over years of principal investing.\r\n      </p>\r\n      <p>In particular it provides business planning services, identification and analysis of the best opportunities for value creation as well as growth capital fundraising services.\r\n      </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n','frontend','en','',0),(3329,'page_meta_title_food','','','page','en','',0),(3330,'page_title_food','Alimentare','Alimentare','page','it','',0),(3331,'page_content_food','','','page','it','',0),(3332,'page_meta_description_food','','','page','it','',0),(3333,'page_meta_keywords_food','','','page','it','',0),(3334,'page_meta_title_food','','','page','it','',0),(3335,'page_title_service-companies','Service companies','Service companies','page','en','',0),(3336,'page_content_service-companies','','','page','en','',0),(3298,'block_content_36','<div class=\"custom-block investment-item realestate\">\r\n            <div class=\"icon-title\">\r\n                <i></i>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500